/*

This test allows testing the DEMUX spi reading.

 It has 3 sub-tests:

    1. read registers

    2. read a single user-defined register

    3. read a single user-defined register

  Expected Result: 

    . the reading in 1. have predefined values

    . The reading in 2. has a predefined value

    . The reading in 3. has a predefined value

*/

/*
  select the DEMUX SPI Link
     .cs_select: 0: DEMUX, 1: RAS
*/
cs_select = 0;
sendToDRELinkBoard_ConfigureSPI_CS(cs_select);

/*
  sub-test1 : read 16 register value of the Pulse Shaping table
  Expected values:  see .vhd code
*/
sendToDREReadRegisters(0x0800, 16)

/*
  sub-test2 : read the "SQ2 LockPoint offset" register value
  Expected value: return = 0
*/
sendToDREReadRegister(0x0423)

/*
  sub-test2 : read the "REG version" register value
  Expected value: return = DF
*/
sendToDREReadRegister(0x6001)
